<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Video Dokumentasi – Admin Lapas</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
  <style>
    .video-preview { margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 5px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border: 1px solid #ccc; background: #000; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="admin-wrapper">
  <%- include('_sidebar') %>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="topbar-title"><h2>🎥 Video Dokumentasi</h2><p>Kelola video kegiatan harian untuk ditampilkan di layar publik</p></div>
      <div class="topbar-actions"><a href="/" target="_blank" class="btn-public">🌐 Lihat Publik</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-area">
      <% if (success) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-success">✅ Video berhasil diunggah dan diperbarui.</div>
      <% } %>
      <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger">❌ <%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header"><h3>Upload Video Baru</h3><p>Maksimal ukuran file 50 MB. Format yang didukung: MP4, WebM.</p></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <form method="POST" action="/admin/video/update" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
              <label>Pilih File Video Baru</label>
              <input type="file" name="video" accept="video/mp4,video/webm" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">📤 Upload & Simpan</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header"><h3>Pratinjau Video Saat Ini</h3><p>Video ini diputar otomatis tanpa suara pada menu layar publik (looping)</p></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <% if (data && data.video_path) { %>
            <video src="<%= data.video_path %>" controls autoplay muted loop class="video-preview"></video>
          <% } else { %>
            <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #888; font-style: italic; border: 1px dashed #ccc; border-radius: 5px;">
              Belum ada video yang diunggah. Placeholder video digunakan di tampilan publik.
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
